1. *Govore* da je ona prelijepa. (They say she is very beautiful.) 
2. Oni *govore* jezik koji ja ne razumijem. (They speak a language I don't understand.)
3. Ona *govori* o tome sa oduševljenjem. (She speaks of it with enthusiasm.)
4. Mi *govorimo* o mnogim stvarima. (We talk about many things.) 
5. Oni su *govorili* o tome satima. (They spoke about it for hours.) 
6. Ja *govorim* vam o tome jer je to važno. (I'm talking to you about it because it's important.)